    Source for Google analytics unsampled report. For unsampled report, the minimum unit of querying range is date. To increase # of partition use hour on "source.querybased.watermark.type" and have "source.querybased.partition.interval" as 23 This will make each partition to have only one day in each query. (Note that, by design, # of max partition is limited by "source.max.number.of.partitions").
